snippet.textDisplay:
Awesome Job!!!!

 Attaullah Esakhelwi really deserved to be a legend of Pak-Music industry.

And Sanwal, man he really did a fantastic job. He is a brilliant talent and i really hope this talent will not disappear too soon. He need to work on new songs to hone his skills, gain more experience and then give us some masterpieces of his own.  

And Coke Studio really is a fine place to discover and present new talents and provide us with good music.

Speaking the truth, at the start, this season disappointed me , I liked coke studio that gave me some different from usual music , something unique, but i didn't really found that in this season. But later that flaw was ignored because of the skills the singers showed, especially by Javed Bashir and Akbar Ali in "Naina Moray", and the unique voice of QB, sweet voice of Hina Nasrullah & great voice of Amanat Ali,  and now this one. 

 But i still hope that  Coke Studio will do better in the next few episodes.

Good Luck!!!

And another compliment from me:

                                                           This Song was really really good

snippet.textDisplay:
Sab maya hai , sab dhalti phirti chaya hai
Is ishq mein hum nay jo khooya jo paya hai
Jo tum nay kaha hai, Faiz nay jo farmaya hai

Sab maya hai

Haan gahay gahay deed ke doulat haath aayi
Ye aik woh lazat naam hai jis ka ruswayi
Bas us kay siwa tu jo bhi sawab kamaya hai

Sab maya hai

Ik naam tu baqi rehta hai, gar jaan nahien 
Jab daikh liya is sooday mein nuqsaan nahien
Tab shama pay dainay jaan patanga aaya hai

Sab maya hai

Maloom hmain sab qais miyaan ka qissa bhi
Sab aik say hain, yeah Ranjha bhi, yeh Insha bhi
Farhad bhi jo ik nahar si khood kay laya hai

Sab maya hai

Kiyon dard kay naamay likhtay likhtay raat karoon
Jis saat samandar par ke naar ke baat karoon
Us naar say koi aik nay dhoka khaya hai?

Sab maya hai

Jis goori pay hum aik ghazal har shaam likhain
Tum jantay ho, hum kiyonkar us ka naam likhain
Dil us ke chookhat chom kay wapis aaya hai

Sab maya hai

Woh larki bhi jo chaand nagar ki raani thi
Woh jis ke alhaar ankhoon mein hayraani thi
Aa us nay bhi pay'ghaam yeehi bhijwaya hai

Sab maya hai

Jo loug abhi tak naam wafa ka laytay hain
Woh jaan kay dhokhay khatay, dhokay daitay hain
Haan thook baja kay hum nay hukam lagaya hai

Sab maya hai

Jab daikh liya har shakhas yahaan harjayi hai
Is shehar say door aik kutiya hum nay banayi hai
Aur us kutiya kay maathay pay likhwaya hai

Sab maya hai

(Poet: Ibn-e-Insha)

I watched this episode a little late as I was busy in my best friend's wedding and today when I finally watched it, I was spellbound. I read someone's comment on Sanwal's picture on coke studio's facebook page that he is a parchi and an extremely bad singer. I had that thing in my mind until I ACTUALLY heard his voice.

Sanwal, if you are reading this, I am a FAN. You may have come here because of your father but you are so going a long way from here because you are seriously talented. Thank you for existing, man!
